main event: Multiple sightings of a bright green object with a developed trail, similar to a meteor, over Alamogordo, Las Cruces, White Sands, and Holloman AFB in New Mexico.
interesting points: The object was initially observed at a high altitude and suddenly developed a trail.
Another similar bright green object, almost the same size as the first, was also reported.
The descriptions of the objects were similar to a meteor.
Civilian and military observers from multiple locations reported the sightings.
The investigation officer concluded that the objects were likely at a greater distance and altitude than the observers initially suspected.
sighted object: Bright green object with a developed trail
location: Alamogordo, Las Cruces, White Sands, and Holloman AFB, New Mexico
